{"tid":2003074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"50年前今日，美國肯特州大學發生五四屠殺","createTime":"2020-05-05T14:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T14:38:44.000Z","uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"63aad0b53b3c1fe27f0d3edd2b91c3f1c4727fdf","tid":2003074,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T14:22:12.000Z","msg":"肯特州立大學槍擊案（也稱五&middot;四屠殺或肯特州立大學屠殺）[1][2][3]於1970年5月4日（星期一）發生在美國俄亥俄州肯特城肯特州立大學。當時國民警衛隊向騷亂學生在13秒內射出67發子彈，造成4名學生死亡，9名學生受傷，其中一人終身殘廢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%82%AF%E7%89%B9%E5%B7%9E%E7%AB%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6%E6%9E%AA%E5%87%BB%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%2582%25AF%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%25B7%259E%25E7%25AB%258B%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25A6%25E6%259E%25AA%25E5%2587%25BB%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6&d=h%2B9cq0gO3qQVjfypIz7KRHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=d213d01b\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%82%AF%E7%89%B9%E5%B7%9E%E7%AB%8B%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6%E6%9E%AA%E5%87%BB%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6</a>"},{"pid":"d2bd0dd87afc377c432722b59f5b8799cb36d940","tid":2003074,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T14:36:01.000Z","msg":"你去返大6叫雞算啦"},{"pid":"b4b807366d84df6cd3c3781f2b9774d464142496","tid":2003074,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T14:38:44.000Z","msg":"事後，開槍被總統特別調查委員會認定是沒有必要，不可原諒的。在隨後的審判中，法院判定俄亥俄州州政府需向原告支付675,000美元賠償，並且做出公開道歉。"}]}